WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.500
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.835 --> 00:00:02.505
I'm excited.

00:00:02.505 --> 00:00:05.187
I have some things on my heart here.

00:00:05.187 --> 00:00:16.342
You know, I felt like I've jumped around so much through so many different videos that I need to make just one video right now.

00:00:16.618 --> 00:00:26.595
Some of this is just a recap; I'm just going over some things that I've already talked about, but I'm making this video for people about the end-time revival.

00:00:26.595 --> 00:00:27.924
I hope this blesses you.

00:00:27.924 --> 00:00:30.920
I know there's a lot of this that you all have already heard.

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:32.000
Hopefully, it's not boring to you.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:39.592
I don't think talking about the glory of God is boring, but if this isn't what you want, I have tons of other videos down below you can watch.

00:00:39.880 --> 00:00:41.032
So here you go.

00:00:41.032 --> 00:00:50.135
I saw a massive wave on the edge of heaven, and it was looking like a massive tidal wave, and it was going like this.

00:00:50.420 --> 00:00:57.695
I asked the Lord—whenever this was right at the Tribulation when I went into Tribulation with him—I said, 'Lord, what is that massive wave?

00:00:57.695 --> 00:01:01.244
' And he said, 'That is a final last push.

00:01:01.244 --> 00:01:05.120
' It was like a glory over it; it was a last outpouring.

00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:18.774
It was like a full manifestation of the glory—a tidal wave of the glory of God was going to pour out over the earth—and he said, 'It's at its breaking point; it's about to dump over.

00:01:18.774 --> 00:01:26.030
' I saw behind the wave all these angels, and they had chariots of fire.

00:01:26.030 --> 00:01:28.960
They had no wings; they all had armor on.

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:40.333
They all had these headdresses on—it looked like Roman headdresses, you know, with the thing right here—and it went down on their face like this.

00:01:40.720 --> 00:01:47.451
They had full armor on, and they had a kilt-like thing, and it was all leather on them, it looked like.

00:01:47.663 --> 00:01:49.1000
They had these shin guards; they had all of it.

00:01:49.1000 --> 00:01:51.227
They were all decked out.

00:01:51.520 --> 00:02:01.920
They had a spear in one hand, and they were holding the reins of the chariot of fire in the other, but there weren't any horses; it was a chariot of fire.

00:02:02.560 --> 00:02:09.200
On the back of the chariot, there was like a little box that had a present; it was a bow.

00:02:09.615 --> 00:02:18.673
Each one of these presents was perfectly made—it looked like a different color for every box—and it had a bow and a ribbon on it.

00:02:18.895 --> 00:02:24.720
I asked the Lord, 'What are those boxes on the back of those chariots of fire?

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:32.160
' And he said to me, 'Those are end-time giftings that have never been seen on the earth before.

00:02:32.160 --> 00:02:37.559
Those are mantles that are going to be given—special giftings for the end-time church.

00:02:37.559 --> 00:02:41.840
' He said they're going to be distributed throughout the world.

00:02:42.570 --> 00:02:52.413
There were hundreds of chariots of fire; it was all behind the water, this massive wave, this massive outpouring.

00:02:53.408 --> 00:03:15.867
To my right, I could see silos, and there were these massive silos full of legs and eyes and body parts, and the angels of the Lord were getting ready to bring those body parts for creative miracles for the last outpouring of the Spirit of God upon this earth.

00:03:16.200 --> 00:03:25.114
I saw the angels, and it was full of legs and arms and noses and ears and eyes and everything you can imagine.

00:03:25.114 --> 00:03:40.840
I'm trying to tell you of anything that you ever believed, but there was not just one color of eye; there was brown eyes and green eyes and blue eyes and black eyes and all kinds of colors of eyes and all kinds of colors of skin and pigments.

00:03:40.840 --> 00:03:43.120
It was full of these parts.

00:03:43.500 --> 00:03:47.713
Then I saw the angels with massive baskets full of finances.

00:03:47.713 --> 00:04:13.640
I could see bicycles that people were believing for on the earth—which, you know, I heard somebody talk in the comments of my video saying that bicycles represent individual ministry; I don't know, it could be a type and shadow or something like that, I have no idea; all I know is that's what I saw—and I saw these baskets full of money: huge amounts of gold, huge amounts of silver.

00:04:14.600 --> 00:04:22.652
The angels were pouring it out on top of the earth, and they were dumping those baskets on the earth.

00:04:23.064 --> 00:04:27.629
Then I saw the Lord—he told me—and the earth was moving.

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:32.291
Everybody wants to talk about a flat earth; it's not real, and flat earth is not...

00:04:32.291 --> 00:04:32.554
it's actually moving.

00:04:41.027 --> 00:04:41.360
I saw the earth, and the earth was moving before me, and it was massive, like we see on TV and stuff.

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:45.048
It was moving, and I could see all of the lights on the earth.

00:04:45.252 --> 00:04:46.275
I said, 'What are those?

00:04:46.275 --> 00:04:52.440
' And he said, 'That's souls that are going to be saved in this last push for revival.

00:04:52.440 --> 00:05:02.500
' I'm showing this and I could see Asia, and there were streams of gold all through Asia—all in China and all in North Korea.

00:05:02.500 --> 00:05:09.365
There were souls, you could see them, and all in South Korea, Vietnam, and the Philippines.

00:05:09.365 --> 00:05:10.505
You could see it.

00:05:10.790 --> 00:05:11.832
Then I saw Jesus.

00:05:11.832 --> 00:05:18.230
He had a tear in his eye, and he told me, 'My gospel cost them something.

00:05:18.230 --> 00:05:21.502
' He said, 'Do you see what's going on in Asia?

00:05:21.502 --> 00:05:23.439
' And I said, 'Yes, Lord, I see it.

00:05:23.439 --> 00:05:25.389
' And it was so precious to his heart.

00:05:25.389 --> 00:05:27.971
He said, 'The gospel cost them something.

00:05:27.971 --> 00:05:30.740
' This was very precious to him.

00:05:30.1000 --> 00:05:35.420
He could see the other people, but his heart was towards Asia a lot.

00:05:35.420 --> 00:05:57.346
I could see all throughout the Middle East and Pakistan and all those areas—the people who are being persecuted so hard for the word; Saudi Arabia, those places like that—I could see that, and his heart was so full of joy because people were standing for the gospel and getting born again, and it was a great sacrifice for them.

00:06:00.806 --> 00:06:03.916
Now I'm going to take you to another part.

00:06:04.387 --> 00:06:11.387
I saw another part of this last outpouring, and the Lord showed this to me, but this was at a separate time.

00:06:11.387 --> 00:06:13.171
I saw people in St.

00:06:13.171 --> 00:06:14.074
Louis, Missouri.

00:06:14.074 --> 00:06:19.180
He showed me Missouri, and I could see all the people gathered on a street corner.

00:06:19.180 --> 00:06:20.479
It was downtown St.

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:23.247
Louis, and I could see a man in a wheelchair.

00:06:23.693 --> 00:06:35.860
There was an African-American man and his wife, an African-American woman, and they laid hands and prayed for this man in a wheelchair.

00:06:35.860 --> 00:06:41.179
He was a white man, and they laid hands on him, and the power of God hit him.

00:06:41.439 --> 00:06:44.754
The man stood up out of the wheelchair and got healed.

00:06:44.754 --> 00:06:53.143
Well, when it did, it sent—you know, whenever you see a shock wave of something—it went boom, like a shock wave in the spirit realm.

00:06:53.605 --> 00:07:00.044
Everyone around that radius of that area started falling out in the glory of God.

00:07:00.044 --> 00:07:04.560
The power of God was just knocking them down; they would just fall on their face.

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:14.847
The power of God started falling in that area, and everyone around that area started weeping underneath the power of God, and they were all radically changed.

00:07:14.847 --> 00:07:21.310
They're all born again because of two people being obedient, a husband and a wife.

00:07:21.310 --> 00:07:31.1000
They just prayed for a man and the power of God hit him and he got up, but everyone around there experienced the glory of God, and it was like a tidal wave of his presence all in that area.

00:07:32.280 --> 00:07:36.440
The Lord told me, 'What you're about to see is like...

00:07:36.440 --> 00:07:40.373
' He said, 'I want you to go in and watch popcorn pop in a pan.

00:07:40.373 --> 00:07:46.498
' So I got some popcorn kernels and some coconut oil and I threw it in there, and I was making it for my little girl.

00:07:46.742 --> 00:07:49.027
He said, 'Do you see those kernels?

00:07:49.027 --> 00:07:57.340
' They were boiling; they were moving around and sizzling, and they were getting ready—you could see they were about to pop, but you didn't know which one was about to pop.

00:07:57.340 --> 00:07:59.896
And he said, 'Do you see those kernels down there?

00:08:00.479 --> 00:08:03.208
You don't know which one's going to pop first, do you?

00:08:03.208 --> 00:08:04.599
' And I said, 'No.

00:08:04.599 --> 00:08:07.280
' He said, 'That's the way the end-time revival is going to be.

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:12.560
' He said, 'It will not be controlled by humans; it will not be able to...

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:14.485
you won't know where it's going to happen next.

00:08:14.485 --> 00:08:17.280
' He said, 'Because it's going to happen like popcorn.

00:08:17.280 --> 00:08:20.773
' He said, 'The next kernel's going to pop, the next kernel's going to pop.

00:08:20.773 --> 00:08:25.830
' And he said, 'That's the way it's going to be, just like the revival that happened at the college, Asbury.

00:08:25.830 --> 00:08:31.374
' He said, 'It's going to be like that; it will pop up and fade away, and people won't talk about it anymore.

00:08:31.374 --> 00:08:32.928
' But he said, 'It's going to happen like that.

00:08:32.928 --> 00:08:38.399
' And he said, 'At the beginning, it's just one little kernel and just one little thing, Brandon.

00:08:38.399 --> 00:08:39.706
' But he said, 'Watch it.

00:08:39.706 --> 00:08:45.336
' And then the next one, and then the next one, and then next thing you know, the whole pan's popping, popping, popping.

00:08:47.669 --> 00:09:03.194
There's so many going on that there's no way to know which one's going to happen next, but it's all popping until the earth was full of the glory of God and the popping of the popcorn—but it's the popping of the Holy Ghost, popping of revivals all throughout the world.

00:09:03.194 --> 00:09:13.326
You're not going to know which one is going to happen next, but the glory of God is going to manifest in a way that we've never seen it before, and it's going to radically change this world.

00:09:13.326 --> 00:09:17.728
I'm telling you, I've seen it: manifestations of the glory of God.

00:09:17.976 --> 00:09:22.664
He told me, and I saw his hand come out of heaven, and there were shafts of light.

00:09:22.940 --> 00:09:29.929
He told me, 'These will be major hotspots for the glory of God, for my presence in the last days.

00:09:29.929 --> 00:09:44.789
' And he said, 'You will know where the major hotspots will be, for there are great satanic strongholds that have tried to be built up around those areas because they know—they've seen it since the testing of time.

00:09:44.789 --> 00:09:46.955
' 'I've had these places picked out, Brandon.

00:09:46.955 --> 00:09:58.646
' He said, 'It's not just something new; I've known this is what I've predestined to come to pass, the manifestation of what I want for the last outpouring.

00:09:58.646 --> 00:10:18.580
' And there were these big dumb devils all gathered around those places, trying to chant, doing their stupid stuff, trying to stop the manifestation, trying to hold back the power and the manifestation of what God's trying to do.

00:10:18.580 --> 00:10:20.959
But oh, how are they so dumb!

00:10:20.959 --> 00:10:24.200
There's no one going to be able to stop this last move.

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:30.600
I don't care how big you think you are; God is going to plow you over like a steamroller.

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:35.816
There's nobody going to stop this revival; God's going to have his way in this earth.

00:10:35.816 --> 00:10:40.994
I saw Branson, Missouri—a great revival happening in Branson.

00:10:41.816 --> 00:10:42.984
I saw Kentucky.

00:10:42.984 --> 00:10:49.939
I saw it on the Eastern Seaboard, around the North Carolina and South Carolina area, all in through that area.

00:10:49.939 --> 00:10:52.113
I saw a great revival happening.

00:10:52.665 --> 00:11:03.454
It's not that it's not going to happen all over the place, but the Lord said, 'A lot of this last revival will not be inside of the major four walls of a building.

00:11:03.454 --> 00:11:05.399
' He said, 'I'm going to do it in Walmart.

00:11:05.399 --> 00:11:07.773
I'm going to do it in the grocery stores.

00:11:07.773 --> 00:11:18.227
I'm going to bring the great revival all throughout America and around the world, just in the streets, just in the parks, just in wherever I tell you—at a bus stop.

00:11:18.227 --> 00:11:20.680
' It doesn't have to be at a church.

00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:29.995
He said, 'It's going to be me manifesting in my people in a way that is like you were in the Book of Acts.

00:11:29.995 --> 00:11:32.952
' So, I saw it happening like that.

00:11:32.952 --> 00:11:36.236
I saw I-35 in the central part of America.

00:11:36.236 --> 00:11:43.395
I saw millions of people coming to the central part of America, and they were all coming by the millions.

00:11:43.700 --> 00:11:52.600
There were so many people that were coming here because of natural disaster—there's a big event that happens before the revival, a great shaking.

00:12:01.576 --> 00:12:01.959
There's a great shaking coming.

00:12:01.959 --> 00:12:06.933
So when this happens, I saw all these people coming to central parts of America.

00:12:06.933 --> 00:12:12.659
There's so many people there's no houses to rent, there's not enough hotels, so people have tents.

00:12:13.179 --> 00:12:18.040
The tents are all the same, so I know it has to be some kind of government-issued tent—unless the church buys them, I don't know.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:32.655
I don't want to assume; it's just me talking to y'all.

00:12:32.655 --> 00:12:44.800
There's fields full of tents, like the hippie movement of people coming just for the revival and trying to get a touch from the Lord.

00:12:50.346 --> 00:12:50.595
I saw glory domes.

00:12:50.595 --> 00:13:00.631
There were massive glory domes where these pillars of light were at, and everyone that comes into those glory domes—not one person touches them—they are healed by the power of God.

00:13:15.411 --> 00:13:15.663
They are touched by the power of God.

00:13:20.408 --> 00:13:22.335
I saw their arms grow out; they come through that glory dome and their arms or their legs or their eyes, everything instantaneously.

00:13:22.335 --> 00:13:25.488
If you're blind, you're healed by the power of God.

00:13:25.488 --> 00:13:26.480
It's a last...

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:32.626
he told me, 'I will not share my glory anymore with man about what's about to happen.

00:13:32.626 --> 00:13:39.805
' He said, 'In the '50s and in the tent revivals, there was always a man there that got a lot of the glory.

00:13:39.805 --> 00:13:42.620
' They always like A.

00:13:42.620 --> 00:13:42.920
A.

00:13:42.920 --> 00:13:47.780
Allen and these people; they always say, 'Oh man, let's look at them.

00:13:47.780 --> 00:13:50.919
' He said, 'But Brandon, I will not allow that to happen anymore.

00:14:02.920 --> 00:14:03.800
I am going to get all the glory, all the praise, and all the honor, for I am a good God and I am a holy God, and there will be a major move of my presence upon this earth.

00:14:21.470 --> 00:14:21.741
I'm telling you all, I hope you're ready because we're about to see something that a lot of you never believed we would, but it's going to be a massive move of God.

00:14:21.741 --> 00:14:22.826
Now, will everybody see it?

00:14:22.826 --> 00:14:36.199
There'll be a lot of scoffers; there'll be a lot of people that mock it and try to come against it and say, 'This isn't a move of God.

00:14:36.199 --> 00:14:49.600
' There'll be the Pharisees in the corner with their little devil horns, saying, 'God's not doing anything in the earth; see, this is all made-up charismatic flakiness.

00:14:49.600 --> 00:14:55.359
' But the Lord told me, 'I am going to bring the walls of religion down.

00:14:55.359 --> 00:15:03.040
' There will be no Baptist, there will be no Methodist, there will be no Catholic or Church of Christ.

00:15:03.040 --> 00:15:11.536
He said, 'I'm going to make it into a unified body, all doing what God's called us to do, and that's to save the lost, bringing forth the harvest.

00:15:11.536 --> 00:15:17.435
' You know, I will describe it like this—and I said this before—it's similar to 9/11.

00:15:17.435 --> 00:15:32.120
Not saying it will be an event like 9/11, but it was similar how everybody was so patriotic and together, running to the churches when everybody was so freaked out whenever the Twin Towers happened and all the stuff with the terror.

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:36.720
He said that there was so much unity there for about six months or so.

00:15:36.720 --> 00:15:41.948
This is the same kind of movement in the body of Christ that's going to happen again.

00:15:41.948 --> 00:15:46.335
It will be the same kind of move, but even greater.

00:15:50.469 --> 00:15:59.399
I wanted to give a recap of everything that the Lord has shown me about these revivals, about the massive things that happened in North Korea.

00:16:02.708 --> 00:16:02.944
A massive revival happened in North Korea.

00:16:02.944 --> 00:16:05.657
I saw angels coming out of the sky.

00:16:05.657 --> 00:16:24.279
I saw stars falling upon the earth, but the Lord said, 'I'm sending my angel armies, and they're coming down and getting all the people in North Korea saved and South Korea,' and they were bringing liberation for the people of North Korea from all their oppression of the demonic government there.

00:16:24.279 --> 00:16:27.875
I saw a massive amount of awesome stuff happening.

00:16:27.875 --> 00:16:32.305
Jesus Christ is fixing to do something huge, and I want you to be a part of it.

00:16:32.305 --> 00:16:35.999
If you're not born again, you need to get born again.

00:16:35.999 --> 00:16:43.433
If you're not filled with the Holy Ghost, you should get filled with the Holy Ghost.

00:16:43.433 --> 00:16:45.720
I'm going to pray for you.

00:16:47.159 --> 00:16:51.184
We're going to believe God; you're going to get baptized in the Holy Ghost.

00:16:51.184 --> 00:16:54.720
If you're believing for healing, let's start it today.

00:16:54.720 --> 00:16:57.248
Faith is now.

00:16:57.248 --> 00:16:58.698
It's not 'we're believing for...

00:16:58.698 --> 00:16:59.927
'; faith is an act.

00:16:59.927 --> 00:17:00.753
Faith is now.

00:17:01.306 --> 00:17:05.182
We're not going to believe for tomorrow because we're believing for it now.

00:17:07.665 --> 00:17:11.919
Now faith is the substance of things hoped for and evidence of things not seen.

00:17:29.426 --> 00:17:29.720
Now faith is not tomorrow; now is like my little girl says all the time: 'Daddy, we're believing for Megan's healing, not tomorrow, not the next day, but we're believing for it now.

00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:32.044
' We're believing for the manifestation now.

00:17:32.044 --> 00:17:37.822
We're believing for Megan to talk and do all the things that we need her to do now.

00:17:37.822 --> 00:17:45.497
My little girl says that all the time to me: 'Dad, we're not praying for tomorrow; we're praying for today.

00:17:45.497 --> 00:17:50.267
' Stretch your hands out right now; just believe it.

00:17:50.267 --> 00:18:00.799
Father, right now in the name of Jesus, I come before you boldly into that throne, and I say in the name of Jesus, these people are delivered.

00:18:02.560 --> 00:18:07.480
I bind and cast out every devil that's binding them, hurting them, or harming them in any way.

00:18:07.480 --> 00:18:15.450
Perversion of all kinds, I speak to you demonic strongholds: you come out of them now in Jesus' name!

00:18:16.543 --> 00:18:18.234
Be free from that demonic stronghold.

00:18:18.234 --> 00:18:24.509
Come out of their body now in Jesus' name.

00:18:25.185 --> 00:18:33.885
I curse you by the power of God, devil, and I say in the name of Jesus, you are free from that demonic stronghold.

00:18:33.885 --> 00:18:36.860
Come out of them in Jesus' name!

00:18:37.540 --> 00:18:42.240
You are free, for whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:18:42.889 --> 00:18:46.314
I speak healing and wholeness and deliverance over your bodies.

00:18:46.700 --> 00:18:50.154
I speak for blind eyes to be opened.

00:18:52.268 --> 00:18:54.580
I speak for ears to be opened right now.

00:19:08.086 --> 00:19:08.423
I speak for your heart to be restored.

00:19:19.395 --> 00:19:19.730
I speak for your legs and arthritis to go away.

00:19:25.440 --> 00:19:28.822
I speak for your brain and fogginess of thinking, and depression and anxiety and fear be broken off of your life!

00:19:28.822 --> 00:19:30.628
Strongholds be broken!

00:19:30.628 --> 00:19:34.600
I speak to asthma in people's bodies.

00:19:34.600 --> 00:19:42.751
I speak to chronic pain: I say go in the name of Jesus!

00:19:54.658 --> 00:20:03.893
I call you healed and whole and well by the power of the blood of Jesus.

00:20:03.893 --> 00:20:06.373
By his stripes, you're healed.

00:20:06.373 --> 00:20:12.811
By his stripes, you're whole, and I call you delivered from sickness and disease.

00:20:12.811 --> 00:20:25.286
I call you delivered from poverty and lack and not enough and barely getting by; I command it to go out of your life in Jesus' name!

00:20:25.286 --> 00:20:27.537
I call deliverance of finances.

00:20:27.537 --> 00:20:31.786
I call a harvest of finances into your life.

00:20:31.786 --> 00:20:41.260
Father, I believe we receive right now every need met, every bondage broken off of their lives in Jesus' name.

00:20:41.260 --> 00:20:43.725
Father, we thank you, Lord.

00:20:43.725 --> 00:20:45.000
You're an awesome God.

00:21:03.279 --> 00:21:03.960
You're faithful to do that which you promised.

00:21:03.960 --> 00:21:50.834
Father, I thank you, Lord, we stagger not at the promise of God through unbelief, but we're strong in faith, giving glory to God, being fully persuaded that what you've promised you're able also to perform.

00:21:50.834 --> 00:22:14.020
I thank you, Father, what you've promised us, Lord, you're able also to perform it.

00:22:14.020 --> 00:22:29.693
I'm believing for these people right now for deliverance in their bodies.

00:22:29.693 --> 00:22:38.440
I believe it, God; you're a healer.

00:22:38.440 --> 00:22:46.110
Have mercy on us.

00:22:46.120 --> 00:23:16.120
Just like blind Bartimaeus, we say, 'Jesus, Son of David, have mercy on us!

00:23:16.120 --> 00:24:25.869
' Just like the woman with the issue of blood, we press forth, we go through there, and we grab onto that hem of his garment, and as she said, 'If I could just touch his hem, I shall be whole.

00:24:25.869 --> 00:24:37.780
' Lord, we press for that hem right now.

